---
title: Moroccan Chicken & Coconut Stew with Veggies & Garlic Rice
description: This fragrant stew gets its flavour from the delicious Moroccan-inspired curry paste. A mild yet tasty base of onion and coconut
milk is revived with refreshing mint, all on a bed of pillowy garlic rice. Divine!

*Due to recent sourcing
challenges, we’ve replaced
silverbeet with baby spinach
leaves, which may be a little
different to what’s pictured.
Don’t worry, your recipe will
be just as delicious!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/moroccan-chicken-coconut-stew-f85712a7.jpg
